(water bubbling)

00:02.436 --> 00:04.836
(muffled breaths)

00:04.905 --> 00:08.240
(water bubbling)

00:08.242 --> 00:14.813
♪♪♪

00:14.948 --> 00:17.449
<i> Lidia: This is a story</i>
<i> about a four-letter word.</i>

00:17.584 --> 00:20.419
<i> The most dangerous</i>
<i> four-letter word of all.</i>

00:20.421 --> 00:22.387
<i> Fate.</i>

00:22.423 --> 00:24.590
<i> And like most tales</i>
<i> worth telling,</i>

00:24.725 --> 00:26.592
<i> The story involves women.</i>

00:26.727 --> 00:29.595
<i> Three glorious,</i>
<i> complicated sisters.</i>

00:30.731 --> 00:32.264
(insects buzz)

00:32.333 --> 00:35.234
(knitting needles clack)
(rhian sighs)

00:35.236 --> 00:37.469
<i> Lidia: The first sister</i>
<i> was the goddess, nona,</i>

00:37.538 --> 00:39.671
<i> Who spun the thread of life.</i>

00:39.740 --> 00:41.340
<i> She was called upon</i>

00:41.342 --> 00:43.675
<i>When women were in a pregnant</i>
<i> state of bliss.</i>

00:43.711 --> 00:46.545
<i> Or... Crisis.</i>

00:46.614 --> 00:48.480
(needles clunk, loud chomp)

00:48.516 --> 00:50.616
<i> Then there was decima,</i>

00:50.751 --> 00:52.451
<i> Who measured the necessities</i>
<i> of life</i>

00:52.586 --> 00:54.486
<i> With her trusty</i>
<i> measuring rod.</i>

00:54.621 --> 00:56.521
- Yeah.
- (giggling)

00:56.590 --> 00:58.556
<i> Lidia: Finally,</i>
<i> there was atropos,</i>

00:58.592 --> 01:00.959
<i>Also known by her roman name,</i>
<i> morta.</i>

01:02.029 --> 01:05.030
<i> Yep, her name was literally</i>
<i> "death".</i>

01:06.434 --> 01:09.234
<i> Morta was responsible for</i>
<i> cutting the threads of life.</i>

01:09.236 --> 01:11.603
<i> Or in my case,</i>

01:11.605 --> 01:13.605
<i> Cutting threads of my old life</i>

01:13.641 --> 01:16.175
<i>In an attempt to bring myself</i>
<i> back to life.</i>

01:16.310 --> 01:18.042
(vibrator whirs)

01:19.847 --> 01:22.914
(sensual rock music plays)

01:22.983 --> 01:24.782
(vibrator clatters)

01:24.819 --> 01:29.787
♪♪♪

01:29.824 --> 01:31.990
(lidia moans)

01:32.126 --> 01:33.592
(heavy breathing)

01:33.594 --> 01:35.394
- Do I have permission
to take off your shirt?

01:35.529 --> 01:37.362
- I can take off
my own shirt.

01:38.766 --> 01:41.033
♪♪♪

01:41.168 --> 01:43.468
Or we can take off yours.
- Yeah.
- Oh yeah.

01:43.504 --> 01:45.737
(shirt flops to floor)

01:45.806 --> 01:47.205
(gale sighs)

01:47.340 --> 01:49.874
(lips smacking, moans)

01:52.480 --> 01:54.613
(slow exhale)

01:54.615 --> 01:56.381
- Oh!
- Oh, lidia!

01:56.417 --> 01:59.784
- Oh! Oh yes!

01:59.820 --> 02:01.653
Oh! Gale!

02:01.689 --> 02:04.022
<i> (moans) gale!</i>
<i> Eleanor: Mom?</i>

02:04.024 --> 02:06.124
- Gale! (moans)
eleanor and gale: Mom!

02:06.160 --> 02:07.559
(rock music stops abruptly)
- ah! Oh!

02:07.595 --> 02:10.795
