- Thinking of your outlaw
biker?

02:30.184 --> 02:31.950
What was his name? Dale?
- Gale.

02:32.085 --> 02:33.652
- Gale.

02:33.721 --> 02:36.087
(seagulls cry)

02:36.123 --> 02:38.624
