tramp stamp.

02:54.041 --> 02:55.740
- Since when are you
the man police?

02:55.809 --> 02:58.610
- When the man does dangerous
drug deals for funsies,

02:58.679 --> 03:01.346
And you are considering getting
into business with him.

03:01.348 --> 03:04.082
- Uh, our family was in
on said drug deal,

03:04.084 --> 03:06.150
And we aren't dangerous
criminals.

03:06.152 --> 03:07.419
- Yet.

03:07.554 --> 03:09.554
- And while I may have
gotten caught up

03:09.557 --> 03:11.823
