biker thing for a moment,

03:11.892 --> 03:13.926
That moment has passed.
- Clearly.

03:14.061 --> 03:16.894
- How's terry?
- Hmm, pressuring my ass.

03:16.931 --> 03:19.097
- Does he want a baby?
- Hmm.

03:19.166 --> 03:20.399
- Did he propose?

03:20.534 --> 03:22.367
Promise spring wedding
so peonies are in season.

03:22.369 --> 03:24.202
- No, he didn't propose,
it's worse.

03:24.205 --> 03:26.571
He wants to... See me.

03:26.573 --> 03:29.040
Like, all the time.
- Oh, my god.

03:29.109 --> 03:31.977
Because he's in love with you.

03:32.112 --> 03:34.712
- He's trying to break me
of my three-night rule.

03:34.748 --> 03:36.448
A limit on sequential
sleepovers

03:36.450 --> 03:38.683
And never at my place.
His place? Fine.

03:38.719 --> 03:41.019
Cove fm? No problem.
- You're insane.

03:41.154 --> 03:43.121
I don't want terry
manning around my pad

03:43.123 --> 03:44.322
With his man stuff.

03:44.391 --> 03:46.991
A woman's apartment
is sacred ground.

03:46.993 --> 03:48.359
(lawn mower roars)

03:49.396 --> 03:51.362
(shuts engine off)

03:53.133 --> 03:55.601
- Oh apologies,
am I in your way?

03:55.736 --> 03:57.935
How is that you two
are tanning on easy street

03:57.972 --> 03:59.938
