07:54.641 --> 07:56.774
<i> Sammy: Seriously,</i>
<i> why are we all here,</i>

07:56.810 --> 07:58.175
<i> Staring at an old bottle,</i>
<i> like zombies?</i>

07:58.212 --> 08:01.379
- 'cause this is the
finley-cullen vessel of fate.

08:01.448 --> 08:03.381
All: (murmur, chuckle)
- it was aunt felicia's idea,

08:03.517 --> 08:05.550
Couple years before this one
was born.

08:05.685 --> 08:08.586
We all wrote down our fates,
sealed them in this bottle,

08:08.655 --> 08:10.722
And sent it off into
the universe.

08:10.857 --> 08:13.925
- Aka, we took it to the beach,
mom and dad got day drunk,

08:13.994 --> 08:16.460
The tide came in,
and bye-bye vessel of fate.

08:16.497 --> 08:18.763
- This is an omen, okay?

08:18.765 --> 08:20.765
This is like bad luck.
- It's something.

08:20.801 --> 08:22.934
- Maybe it'll contain
sage advice.

08:23.003 --> 08:25.603
Or mini crabs. Let's open it!
- Uh, no!

08:25.605 --> 08:28.139
We promised aunt felicia we'd
let the universe decide.

08:28.141 --> 08:31.342
Now that she's not here--
(wind howls, doors slam)

08:33.080 --> 08:35.279
Rhian: What the...?
Lidia: (gasps) the bottle!

08:35.315 --> 08:36.814
(bottle rumbles)

08:36.850 --> 08:38.683
(glass shatters)
all: Oh!

08:38.685 --> 08:40.384
- Aunt felicia?

08:43.390 --> 08:45.223
As spoken.

08:45.358 --> 08:48.893
<i> Lidia: Ry, come on!</i>
<i> It was the wind!</i>

08:48.896 --> 08:51.462
Gimme those.
- Oh.

08:51.464 --> 08:54.299
Rolled scrolls.
Got a blue one!

08:54.368 --> 08:58.036
- Please remember that I was
always nice to you.

