09:06.413 --> 09:08.379
I knew that fate is nothing
more than a made-up thing

09:08.514 --> 09:10.582
That lazy people use so they
have something to blame

09:10.584 --> 09:12.117
When things go sideways.

09:14.187 --> 09:16.253
- (raeds) "tatted up,
hot girlfriend."

09:16.290 --> 09:18.156
- Ah!
- "funnel beer like a champ.

09:18.291 --> 09:21.126
Never work for the man!"
I've done all these things.

09:21.261 --> 09:23.227
- Yeah!
